1.获取token
 post
 http://localhost:8081/oauth/token?grant_type=password&scope=read_userinfo&username=zzr&password=123456
    header:
    accept:application/json
    content-type:application/x-www-form-urlencoded
    Authorization:Basic Y2xpZW50YXBwOjExMjIzMw==
2.访问资源
get
http://localhost:8081/api/example/hello
header:
authorization:bearer 3735ceb7-752e-42ce-9187-7927299e283e